title: Christmas fruitcake
ingredients: ['175g candied orange peel', '60g coarsely chopped walnuts', '70g raisins', '70g sultanas', '2 tablespoons plain flour', '125g butter, softened', '100g caster sugar', '2 1/2 tablespoons honey', '2 eggs', '1 1/2 tablespoons single cream', '2 tablespoons dark rum', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '200g plain flour', '1/2 teaspoon baking powder']
